QuestData.Title: Trophy of Glory: Khargax the Devourer
QuestData.Description: Defeating Khargax has yielded you a trophy worthy of acclaim.$b$bTake this to Durotan at Beastwatch.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the trophy to Durotan at Beastwatch in Gorgrond.
QuestData.RewardText: The Laughing Skull have always steered clear of that area because Khargax was very quick for such a huge beast. They will be pleased to know their eaten dead have been avenged.
